  </li>
  <li>
    y <%= link_to "mucho mas", "/features" %>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3>
  How can I start using it?
</h3>

<p>
  You can start by reviewing our <%= link_to "pricing plans", "/pricing" %>.  We even have a <%= link_to "free plan", "/pricing/free" %> to get you started without paying a dime.
</p>

<p>
  You will have to <%= link_to "sign up", "/register" %> with <strong><%= getAppName() %></strong>.  Sign up is free and won't take you more than a minute.
</p>

<p>
  Once you have signed up and picked a pricing plan you can start creating your companies, locations, products, and everything you need to manage your sales easily.
</p>

<h3>
  How much does it cost?
</h3>

<p>
  We have several <%= link_to "pricing plans", "/pricing" %>, pick the one that best fits your needs.  We even have a <%= link_to "free plan", "/pricing/free" %> to get you started without paying a dime.  One thing is for sure, you'll be paying less than any other Point of Sale software out there, for a better product with zero installation and zero configuration.  Just sign up, pick a plan and start using it.
</p>

<h3>
  What if I want to get all my information out of <%= getAppName() %>?
</h3>

<p>
  We will never hold your data hostage.  We provide a simple process to export your data into a simple Excel file.
</p>

<h3>
  Will my information be safe?
</h3>

<p>
  We backup your data daily, and if anything should happen, we'll be right there to help you restore it.
</p>

<h3>
  What about privacy?
</h3>

<p>
  We don't share or sell your information.  Ever.  Not even your email address.
</p>